  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 268bf36e2c95048f4b4ca0fcdf827688, type: 3}
  m_Name: BossDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  SpeakerName: Dialogue
  lines:
  - 'Hey there friend you have a lot of tasks to complete on your shift today there
    is a building with some defects that needs addressing. '
  - This list contains issues involving some mechanical issues with a boiler, heat
    pump, and some water pipes.
  - "For electrical issues it seems that the tenants have issues with some outlets
    in some bedrooms, bathrooms, and other areas you\u2019ll have to make sure you
    check out the circuit panels it can help you out with finding the source of the
    issues."
  - "Last but not least are envelope issues some areas of the house weren\u2019t
    properly sealed so you\u2019re going to have to check for any drafts and gaps
    or holes around the house to figure out how to proceed with a resolution. "
  - Here check out the tools available and figure out what is needed to fix the issues
    around the building make sure you take the time to learn what each item does
    so you can make sure you have the right tools.
  - "You can\u2019t work there all day so take into account you\u2019re on a time
    limit!"
